<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Booking Feedback Request</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #666;
        }
        .booking-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .feedback-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .feedback-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>How Was Your Experience?</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for choosing our service. We hope you had a great experience! Would you mind taking a moment to share your feedback?</p>
        
        <div class="booking-details">
            <h3>Booking Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Date & Time:</strong> {{startTime}}</p>
            <p><strong>Duration:</strong> {{duration}} minutes</p>
        </div>

        <center>
            <a href="{{feedbackUrl}}" class="feedback-button">Share Your Feedback</a>
        </center>
        
        <p>Your feedback helps us improve our service for everyone. It will only take a minute!</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Eventide. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
